##### Animations

You can trigger animations directly on an element using *animation-name or .hover-*animation-name 
You can also trigger animation using .mouseenter-*animation-name and .mouseleave-*animation-name behaviors 
on child elements of a parent with a .hover-animate-children class.

##### html
----------

```
<!-- Direct animation trigger -->
<div class="fade-in fast">Fade in fast</div>

<!-- Hover behavior animation trigger -->
<div class="hover-fade-in fast">On hover, fade in fast</div>

<!-- Animate children animation trigger -->
<div class="hover-animate-children">
  <span class="mouseenter-fade-in mouseleave-fade-out fast">
    on mouse enter fade in fast and on mouse leave fade out fast
  </span>
</div>
```

